# Topic 15: Supported Languages ⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Concept

A Databricks notebook supports **Python, SQL, Scala, and R**.

---

## Theory

| Language | Use Case          |
| -------- | ----------------- |
| Python   | ETL, PySpark      |
| SQL      | Analytics         |
| Scala    | Spark Development |
| R        | Data Science      |

Python and SQL are the most commonly used by Data Engineers.

---

## Architecture

```text
Notebook
   │
 ┌─┼──────────────┐
 ▼ ▼ ▼ ▼
Python SQL Scala R
```

---

